  <summary>1/8/2003--Introduced.
Dividend Payment Incentive Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow dividends as a deduction in the case of a C corporation, except in the case of: (1) a regulated investment company; (2) a real estate investment trust; or (3) an exempt corporation.</summary>
